{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538070/extras/header_senses.png?t=1740385790\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mind your surroundings! Keep an ear out for strange noises, and be on the lookout for signs that you\u2019re walking into a trap. Spatial audio allows you to hear the direction of monsters or special items in nearby rooms.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538070/extras/combat.gif?t=1740385790\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538070/extras/header_torch.png?t=1740385790\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The oppressive darkness can be both your foe and your ally. Lighting your torch lets you peer into the next room and see what dangers lurk ahead, and extinguishing it will let you sneak past them. But take care not to reignite it at the wrong moment, lest ye be spotted by the creatures stalking the dungeon.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538070/extras/stealth.gif?t=1740385790\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538070/extras/header_puzzle.png?t=1740385790\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The vast, winding tunnels are riddled with puzzles and clues, beckoning you to explore further and further. Discover the secrets of The Gorge Fortress and uncover its ancient treasures.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3538070/extras/puzzle.gif?t=1740385790\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.